highlights.text: “Ranjha (From "Shershaah")” by Jasleen Royal, B Praak, Romy, and Anvita Dutt is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Bengaluru, up 43 spots at #10.
“Maan Meri Jaan” by King has been on Top Songs Bengaluru the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Bengaluru. “Jhoome Jo Pathaan” is the highest at #4.
“Main Khiladi - From "Selfiee"” by Tanishk Bagchi, Anu Malik, and Abhijeet is the highest new entry on Top Songs Bengaluru at #67.
